Package: simplificar
Type: Package
Title: A high-level API for ggplot2
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Lorenz", "Walthert", 
    email = "lorenz.walthert@icloud.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Lorenz Walthert <lorenz.walthert@icloud.com>
Description: simplificar - for simplify in Spanish - is a high-level
    API for ggplot2 that enables fast experiments. It is envisioned as
    a tool for exploratory analysis early in the cycle of statistical model 
    building where standardized plots should be available quickly, with few
    lines of code.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
